Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,will learn how to use alerts to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.36,0:00:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,make your app better, your users
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.45,0:00:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,happier, and your ratings and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.60,0:00:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,revenues higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Good alerts can accomplish that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,because they are one of the most
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.75,0:00:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,efficient problem-solving tools
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,at your disposal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,They help people enjoy your app,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,and navigate it easily, instead
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.99,0:00:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,of getting stuck in some
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.35,0:00:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,suboptimal state, getting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.31,0:00:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,frustrated, confused, quitting
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.98,0:00:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,your app, de-installing your
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.61,0:00:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,app, and giving you one-star
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.31,0:00:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,ratings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.71,0:00:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you create alerts that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.10,0:00:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,work?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.29,0:00:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you get to the creating
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.92,0:01:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,part, you should ask yourself a
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.85,0:01:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,very important question.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.10,0:01:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I be using an alert at
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.01,0:01:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,all?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.23,0:01:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the best way to achieve
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,my goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.68,0:01:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look at some examples of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.47,0:01:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,good alert use.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The most common one you are
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,familiar with is to correct
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.61,0:01:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,errors, like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.57,0:01:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Alerts are also used to request
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.84,0:01:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,access to user data, such as
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,contacts, location, or financial
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.16,0:01:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,information.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.96,0:01:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We provided a format for your
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.40,0:01:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,use, and put a lot of thought in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.54,0:01:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,its content.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It explains concisely and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.84,0:01:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,clearly what data is requested,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and how it will be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.75,0:01:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Alerts are also used to notify
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,people of major updates, such as
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.95,0:01:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,significant feature releases, or
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.15,0:01:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,critical security fixes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.59,0:01:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,These announcements should be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.90,0:01:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,used judiciously and sparingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.81,0:02:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Reserve them only for problems
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that merit immediate attention
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,or features that would really
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,benefit your audience, certainly
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.05,0:02:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,not every update merits an
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,alert, and on that note, let's
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,talk about when alerts should
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,not be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.04,0:02:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I will introduce this topic with
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.62,0:02:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,a very important point I would
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.55,0:02:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,like you to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.68,0:02:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Alerts are disruptive by design.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see I'm in the middle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.07,0:02:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,of a talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you wish you could do this
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.32,0:02:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to all annoying alerts?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So the lesson here is, do not
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.36,0:02:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,use alerts for non-essential
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.18,0:02:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,content.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.69,0:02:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Before putting any content in an
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.57,0:02:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,alert, ask yourself, do people
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,really need to know this, and do
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,they need to know this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,If the answer to that question
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,is not an absolute resounding
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,yes, do not interrupt your
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.50,0:03:01.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The next important point I would
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.38,0:03:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,like you to remember is that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.28,0:03:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,alerts are lightweight by
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.51,0:03:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,design.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Their small format reflects and
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.57,0:03:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,serves the purpose of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.07,0:03:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,facilitating quick, informed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.00,0:03:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,decisions, so that people can
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,make a choice, and move on with
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever they were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.74,0:03:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, do not overload
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,alerts with lengthy content, or
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,too many choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.76,0:03:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,These tasks are better left to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,larger UI elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.83,0:03:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look at some examples.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alerts are not settings, nor are
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.30,0:03:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,they multiple choice questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.51,0:03:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see that the actions are
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,struggling to fit into the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.46,0:03:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,provided format, and here is a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,hint for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.22,0:03:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If your alert takes most of the
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,supported view port, it is time
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.28,0:03:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to cut down or relegate some of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.52,0:03:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the tasks to larger elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Alerts are full-scale diagnostic
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.64,0:04:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not use them to expose
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,technical data, especially error
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,codes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Alerts are not afterthoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not use them to fix
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,preventable problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.24,0:04:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, if you have
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.82,0:04:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,password rules, articulate them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.12,0:04:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,clearly on the main screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.73,0:04:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You can also disallow invalid
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,character input.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the thing to not do is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to make users memorize a long,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,complicated list of characters,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and then go back to fix the
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.14,0:04:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,problem that should not have
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.74,0:04:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,occurred in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To summarize, the dos and don'ts
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of alerts, use them to correct
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,errors, request access to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,customer data, or notify people
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.80,0:04:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,of major updates.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.40,0:04:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not use them for
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.03,0:04:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,non-essential or lengthy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.17,0:04:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,content.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not offer complicated
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:04:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And do not duplicate the tasks
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,of other UI elements.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you have considered all
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,these factors and decided that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.93,0:05:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you need an alert after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.30,0:05:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you go about writing a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.53,0:05:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,successful one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.32,0:05:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It turns out that the structure
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,of the alert, with its clear
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.94,0:05:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,separation of visual elements
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,already sets you on this path of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,success.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back to our good alert
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,example, and see how we can make
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.74,0:05:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,use of that structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,In the title, state your main
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,point in one sentence or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.42,0:05:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In the message details, provide
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,brief additional information if
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,necessary, such as the cause of
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,the error, or the reason for
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.44,0:05:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Offer actions that are easy to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.73,0:05:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,understand and perform.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have to take people
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,outside the app, or to a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.33,0:06:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,different state, make sure to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,navigate them there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.01,0:06:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not leave this job to the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Back button, the Home button,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,the main screen, or otherwise
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,leave users to find their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.63,0:06:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If people scan the title and the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,actions, ideally, they should be
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.88,0:06:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,able to understand what is going
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.45,0:06:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,on without paying too much
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,attention to the message
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.30,0:06:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,details.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,While this is not always
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,possible, it is a good goal to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,aspire to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you need a quick mnemonic
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,rule, a good alert answers three
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.88,0:06:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,key questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.46,0:06:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.86,0:06:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why people are seeing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And how this should proceed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,based on the information they've
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,received.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you've mastered the
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.65,0:06:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,structure of the alert, let's
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.52,0:06:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,practice and apply these
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.60,0:06:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,guidelines to fix some common
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.29,0:06:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's read through this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,"App name" cannot open this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,file.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:06:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The title is accurate, but not
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.89,0:07:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,especially helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Which file do we mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.60,0:07:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,People may be working with
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.61,0:07:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,multiple files.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.85,0:07:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You may need to download the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,latest available updates for the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,app.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.71,0:07:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to visit the "app
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,name" website for more
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.23,0:07:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,information and troubleshooting
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.67,0:07:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,tips?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,These instructions are vague and
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,tentative, and suggest multiple
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,outcomes, and that is also a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of text.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.53,0:07:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Yes. The actions are
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.95,0:07:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,difficult to understand without
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,going back and reading said
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,lengthy instructions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how we can improve
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.59,0:07:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,First, let's specify the file
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,name for clarity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.27,0:07:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, let's pare down the
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.42,0:07:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,instructions for simplicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, let's offer clear
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.02,0:07:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,actionable choices, so that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,people understand what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.12,0:07:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,when they tap on any one of
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.90,0:07:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is your before and after.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.89,0:08:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one do you think looks
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,better?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's take a look at an
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.62,0:08:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,alert that seems to be written
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.79,0:08:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,with all the guidelines in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's read through this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.23,0:08:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancel download?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.82,0:08:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,If you cancel now, you will not
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,receive this file.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.90,0:08:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancel? Okay [laughter].
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.05,0:08:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing wrong with any
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,individual part, the title
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.80,0:08:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,states the question, the message
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.94,0:08:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,describes the consequences, and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,even the actions use the
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.25,0:08:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,recommended terminology.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.09,0:08:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Cancel and okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,However, this is a classic
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,example of a confusing alert
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.65,0:08:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,that happens even to the most
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,experienced developers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So the lesson here is, even when
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,using guidelines, always check
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the result for any ambiguity or
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.01,0:08:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.58,0:08:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see how we can clarify
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.84,0:08:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,First, let's rephrase the title
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to remove ambiguity and mention
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.53,0:09:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,the filename to be more
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.45,0:09:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, let's apply similar
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.43,0:09:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,changes to the message details.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.77,0:09:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And for good measure, let's
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,reiterate the choices and the
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.72,0:09:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,actions, so people understand
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens if they click on
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.41,0:09:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.14,0:09:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is your before and after.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.09,0:09:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hope you would agree that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,the after looks a bit better
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.70,0:09:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,than the before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.32,0:09:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you have learned how to
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,make use of the structure, let's
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,talk a bit about style and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,quality.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.61,0:09:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I have a couple of tips
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.57,0:09:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.21,0:09:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoid platitudes, jargon or
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.42,0:09:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,fillers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.40,0:09:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All they do is take space
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,without adding any return value.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Use correct formatting,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,spelling, and punctuation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.79,0:09:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This seems like a very basic
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,piece of advice, but it will go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,a very long way toward making
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.25,0:10:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,your alerts and your app look
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.45,0:10:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,polished and professional.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.34,0:10:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, consider your audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.09,0:10:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether you are writing for
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,medical professionals, special
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,needs students, or even a very
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.29,0:10:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,smart cat who just learned how
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,to use an iPad, make sure that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.75,0:10:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,your editorial voice matches
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,their needs and expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In conclusion, here are the
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,three simple things you can do
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.79,0:10:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,now to make your alerts awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep them simple and helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.46,0:10:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Go practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.84,0:10:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Take what you learned, go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,through your app, see if you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,need all the alerts that you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.51,0:10:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,created, and if you do, see how
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,you can make them work harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And for more information and an
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in-depth look on how to write
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.22,0:10:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,alerts for iOS and macOS, read
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,the HIG available at the Apple
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.98,0:10:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,website.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:10:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
